para_trans: About celebrating National Men's / Great Men's Birthdays and National Day in 2025.
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
National Men's / Great Men's Birthdays and National Day events in 2025
Celebrations should be held in the ministry and in all government / semi-government offices as per the schedule.
Programmes shown in the Annexure include public holidays, weekly holidays (Saturdays and Sundays) and local
Holidays may be coming and if the Central Government suggests changes in the programme in this regard, the same may be celebrated.
Come, otherwise those events should be celebrated on the same day.
3. Divisional Commissioner / Collector to all Government / Semi-Government in his / her Division / District.
Issue necessary instructions regarding the conduct of the event in the office and their implementation.
